ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of ANDREW WILKINSON of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Roderick John Harris who term has expired.
